<script>
    function addGooglePlacesListener_Customer() {
        var googleAddressLookup = new google.maps.places.Autocomplete(document.getElementById('createCustomerAddressAutocomplete'));
        // Limit returning data
        googleAddressLookup.setFields(['address_components', 'name']);

        googleAddressLookup.addListener('place_changed', function () {
            var place = googleAddressLookup.getPlace();
            var addressMapped = GetAddressMapped(place);

            $('#CustomerName').val(addressMapped.Name);
            $('#CustomerAddress1').val(addressMapped.Address1);
            $('#CustomerAddress2').val(addressMapped.Address2);
            $('#CustomerAddress3').val(addressMapped.Address3);
            $('#CustomerAddress4').val(addressMapped.Address4);
            $('#CustomerPostcode').val(addressMapped.Postcode);
        });
    }

    addGooglePlacesListener_Customer();
    _intlTelInput("#Telephone","Telephone");
    _intlTelInput("#ContactTelephone","ContactTelephone");
</script>


<script>
    $('body').on('change', '#contactSection', function () {
        var firstName = $('#ContactFirstName');
        var requiredFirstName = $('.requiredFirstName');

        firstName.prop('required', false);
        requiredFirstName.hide();

        var targetRequiredFiled = [
            '#ContactLastName', '#ContactPosition', '#ContactEmail', '#ContactTelephone'
        ];

        for (var i = 0; i < targetRequiredFiled.length; i++) {
            if (!isBlank($(targetRequiredFiled[i]).val())) {
                requiredFirstName.show();
                firstName.prop('required', true);
                break;
            }
        }
    });
</script>
